- Use TanStack Query/Mutation hooks; no raw fetch in components.
- Centralize API calls in thin wrappers (src/lib/api/*) and reuse query keys.
- Handle loading/error states via Query results (avoid duplicate spinners).

Refer to documentation and best practices here:
Docs: https://tanstack.com/query/latest/docs/framework/react/overview
